      "rationale": "NHI and RH were selected as primary QoIs. Comparison was performed using percent error between CFD-predicted and experimentally reported central estimates. Mean absolute percent error of 9.4% across five operating points was within the ±15% acceptance band established for MRL 2. Validation metrics are documented in the primary validation result."
